{"title":"Cyclist Track Days 2025 bikes #3: Factor Ostro VAM","link":"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/cyclist-track-days-2025-bikes-factor-ostro-vam","date":1740668967000,"content":"<p><a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk\">Cyclist</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/cyclist-track-days-2025-bikes-factor-ostro-vam\">Cyclist Track Days 2025 bikes #3: Factor Ostro VAM</a></p>\n\n<p>Whether you are in the market for a new bike or just want to try out some of the best bikes in the world, <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/cyclist-track-days-information\">Cyclist Track Days</a> offer a unique experience to test the latest top-end bikes from the leading brands on the market. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>The next bike in our run through of the incredible bikes available to test ride at this years Track Days is the Factor Ostro VAM.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ridden by the Israel-Premier Tech pro team, the Ostro VAM is Factor’s<a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/buying-guides/best-all-round-road-race-bikes\"> all-round racing bike</a>, balancing aero attributes with light weight.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Former <em>Cyclist</em> website editor Matthew Loveridge recently reviewed the latest model of the Factor Ostro VAM and said it was ‘even better than the old one, and it was already phenomenal’, citing its racy ride, real-world usability and value compared to its top tier rivals. The Shimano Dura-Ace spec he tested weighed in at 7.1kg for a size 54.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The bike you’ll be testing at the Cyclist Track Day in Leeds will be built with a SRAM Force AXS groupset, Black Inc 48|58 wheels, which retails for around £9,400.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can read Matthew’s full review <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/reviews/factor-ostro-vam-road-bike-review\">here</a>. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>The Factor Ostro VAM will be at the following Track Days event:</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>7<sup>th</sup> June 2025, The Brownlee Centre, Leeds</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>For more information on Cyclist Track Days click <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/cyclist-track-days-information\">here</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong><a href=\"https://www.eventbrite.com/cc/cyclist-track-days-2025-3855053\" target=\"_blank\">BOOK YOUR TICKET HERE</a></strong></h3>\n\n\n<div>\r\n                <div>\r\n                   <div>\r\n                      <div>\r\n                         <h4><span>Related Posts</span></h4>\r\n                      </div>\r\n                      <div>\r\n                         <div>\r\n                            <div>\r\n                            <article>\r\n                    <div>\r\n                       <h4>\r\n                          <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/cyclist-track-days-2025-bikes-scott-foil-rc\">Cyclist Track Days 2025 bikes #2: Scott Foil RC</a>\r\n                       </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                 </article><article>\r\n                    <div>\r\n                       <h4>\r\n                          <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/cyclist-track-days-2025-bikes-van-rysel-rcr\">Cyclist Track Days 2025 bikes #1: Van Rysel RCR</a>\r\n                       </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                 </article><article>\r\n                    <div>\r\n                       <h4>\r\n                          <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/reviews/factor-ostro-vam-road-bike-review\">Factor Ostro VAM road bike review</a>\r\n                       </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                 </article><article>\r\n                    <div>\r\n                       <h4>\r\n                          <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/cyclist-track-days-information\">Cyclist Track Days 2025 info and how to get tickets</a>\r\n                       </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                 </article><article>\r\n                    <div>\r\n                       <h4>\r\n                          <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/in-depth/not-all-carbon-bikes-are-cre